snippet.title: Tearaway - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
earaway is now available.
Embark on a unique adventure from the creative minds behind LittleBigPlanet™ with your new friend, the adventurous iota or the intrepid atoi — a papercraft messenger from another dimension with a unique message to deliver — to you! Tapping into the full range of PS Vita system's features, Tearaway™ delivers the most immersive and unique experience that only the PS Vita system can deliver.

http://us.playstation.com/psvita/games-and-media/psv-tearaway.html

©2013 Sony Computer Entertainment America. Developed by Media Molecule. Tearaway is a trademark of Sony Computer Entertainment America.
